<p>
<seg id=1> The western tourists, who were just freed from Yemen, said that they were treated as a cover by the kidnappers when the Yemen government army tried to save them and fire at the kidnappers. </seg>
<seg id=2> Four tourists were killed in the fighting on Tuesday, and 12 had a narrow escape. </seg>
<seg id=3> The Yemen government said that the Yemen army fired at the kidnappers when some hostages were obviously going to be killed. </seg>
<seg id=4> But some freed tourists said that the firing started after the Yemen army began the rescue action. </seg>
</p>
